---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About AIBuilderHub"
  description="Who we are, why we built AIBuilderHub, and how we choose which tools to review."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">About AIBuilderHub</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">

      <p>Most reviews of AI tools are useless. They're written by people who've never opened the product, padded with SEO keywords, and ranked based on commission rates rather than actual quality.</p>

      <p>AIBuilderHub exists because solopreneurs, freelancers, and founders deserve better than that when deciding where to spend $20-100/month on tools.</p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>We build real projects with every tool we review - landing pages, SaaS MVPs, automations - and report what actually happens. Including what breaks, what's confusing, and what the marketing page doesn't tell you.</p>

      <h2>Who this is for</h2>
      <p>People who want to build digital products with AI but don't have time to test 30 different platforms. Specifically: solopreneurs launching their first product, freelancers adding AI capabilities to their services, and small business owners who want internal tools without IT budget.</p>

      <h2>How we make money</h2>
      <p>Through affiliate commissions when you click our links and sign up for tools. We disclose this on every article. It doesn't change our rankings - a tool we don't recommend stays off the list regardless of commission rate. See our <a href="/disclosure">full affiliate disclosure</a>.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions, corrections, or want to suggest a tool to review: <strong>hello@aibuilderhub.app</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
